ignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg" alt="鲶鱼和装瓶工（图片来源：Charlie Barclay Harris）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774334" class="wp-caption-text">鲶鱼和装瓶工（图片来源：Charlie Barclay Harris）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">2024 年雷丁和利兹音乐节</a>于昨天（8 月 23 日）在 Richfield Avenue（雷丁）和 Bramham Park（利兹）的惯常举办地拉开帷幕 –<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-how-to-watch-online-and-at-home-3785021">请参阅此处</a>，了解如何在家中通过 BBC iPlayer 和其他地方观看音乐节（如果您无法观看）确保获得门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish And The Bottlemen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>是今年音乐节的六大主角。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">,</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c"> </a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a h